sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / DSP Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics<br/>6060/TCP healthz
    participant CronCtrl as Cron Controller<br/>(in workflow-controller)
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod<br/>(main container)
    participant InitExec as argoexec (init)<br/>Artifact Download
    participant WaitExec as argoexec (wait)<br/>Artifact Upload
    participant S3 as S3 / Minio<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS

    Note over User, DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    K8sAPI-->>WFC: Informer notification<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    WFC->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow Pod<br/>(main + argoexec sidecar)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    K8sAPI-->>InitExec: Pod scheduled

    InitExec->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>InitExec: Artifact data

    Note over Pod: Main container executes<br/>pipeline step logic

    Pod->>WaitExec: Container completes<br/>(emissary /var/run/argo/)

    WaitExec->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>WaitExec: Upload confirmed

    WaitExec->>K8sAPI: Patch WorkflowTaskResult<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer

    K8sAPI-->>WFC: Result notification
    WFC->>K8sAPI: Update Workflow status<br/>Schedule next DAG node
    WFC->>DB: Archive workflow (optional)<br/>Auth: Secret credentials

    Note over User, DB: Flow 2: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    CronCtrl->>K8sAPI: List CronWorkflows<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    K8sAPI-->>CronCtrl: CronWorkflow list
    CronCtrl->>CronCtrl: Check cron schedule
    CronCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow from template<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer

    Note over User, DB: Flow 3: Artifact Garbage Collection

    WFC->>K8sAPI: Create WorkflowArtifactGCTask<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    WFC->>K8sAPI: Create GC Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    Note over S3: GC Pod (argoexec)<br/>deletes expired artifacts
